'''光互連'''是一種[[光通訊|光通訊]]的方式<ref name="register">{{cite news|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/09/23/light_peak/|title=Intel unfurls copper-killing optical cables|last=Myslewski|first=Rik|date=2009-09-23|publisher=The Register|accessdate=2009-09-27|archive-date=2009-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090927152802/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/09/23/light_peak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是用[[光纖|光纖]]或是其他光傳輸介質來在計算機內的各元件或子系統中交換資料。光纖的{{le|頻寬 (運算)|Bandwidth (computing)|頻寬}}比一般導線高很多，從10 Gbit/s到100 Gbit/s<ref name="cnet">{{cite news|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-10360047-264.html|title=Intel's Light Peak: One PC cable to rule them all|last=Shankland|first=Stephen|date=2009-09-23|publisher=CNet|accessdate=2009-09-27|archive-date=2010-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101016001024/http://news.cnet.com/8301-30685_3-10360047-264.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

光互連已被用作電腦和行動設備連線的方式之一<ref name="pcworld">{{cite news|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/172480/intel_connects_pcs_to_devices_using_light.html|title=Intel Connects PCs to Devices Using Light|last=Shah|first=Agam|date=2009-09-23|publisher=[[PC_World_(magazine)|PCWorld]]|accessdate=2009-09-27|archive-date=2009-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090926041118/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/172480/intel_connects_pcs_to_devices_using_light.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也用在電腦的[[主機板|主機板]]及設備上<ref name="cnet" /><ref name="iptronics">{{cite news |url=http://www.iptronics.com/36209/Optical%20interconnects.html |title=Parallel Optical Interconnects |last=Bek |first=Jesper |date=2008-06-09 |publisher=IPtronic |accessdate=2010-04-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305124306/http://www.iptronics.com/36209/Optical%20interconnects.html |archivedate=2011-03-05 }}</ref>。

[[IBM|IBM]]已經建立一個[[波分复用|波分复用]]的光互連通訊協定，若此技術成功，會產生第一個可以{{le|百萬兆等級運算|exascale computing}}（每秒可以處理百萬兆個指令）的電腦<ref>Ross, Valerie. April, 2011. "The Light-Driven Computer". ''Popular Science''. Volume 278, #4, Page 58.</ref>。其中會有[[波导管|波导管]]將八種不同顏色的光束發射到[[調變|調變器]]的七個接口中，因此八個資料可以同時傳送。多波長的光速延著芯片傳播，再利用光學開關來切換方向<ref>"Light-driven plasmonic nanoswitch may pave way for new
computers, tech". http://www.physorg.com/news151345921.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.physorg.com/news151345921.html |date=20110915213828 }}. January 16, 2009. June 8, 2011.</ref>。

